  "body": "# Bug Report\r\n\r\n## Description\r\n\r\n\r\n## Steps to reproduce\r\n1. Go to a 1-1 chat and click 'Fetch more messages'\r\n2. Check the position of the appeared loader and its view\r\n3. Check the loader appeared above the chat's logo\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\n1. The Fetch loader is NOT pixelated\r\n2. The Fetch loader is aligned by height\r\n3. The loader above the chat's logo didn't appear for a moment after fetching is finished\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\n1. The Fetch loader is pixelated\r\n2. The Fetch loader is not aligned by height\r\n3. The loader above the chat's logo appeared for a moment after fetching is finished\r\n<img width=\"352\" alt=\"image\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/14942081/213072405-ecacf538-abe4-4d08-a2cc-ae7355fade4e.png\">\r\nhttps://user-images.githubusercontent.com/14942081/213073050-93f6965c-51fe-4ef4-94c5-f8a09fe75a1a.mov\r\n\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n\r\n- Status desktop version: https://ci.infra.status.im/job/status-desktop/job/release/job/release%252F0.9.x/3/\r\n- Operating System: macOS Monterey\r\n\r\n",
